title.narrative: Lao PDR - Small and Medium Enterprise Access to Finance Project

description.narrative: This project aims at providing long-term funding sources for banks to provide long-term credit to SMEs. The project will support the growth of privately-owned SMEs by increasing the supply of long-term finance provided by commercial banks and by strengthening thecapability of the Department for Small and Medium Enterprise Promotion (DOSMEP) to formulate and implement public policies that promote access to finance for SMEs.
